---
const title = "Sitio en Mantenimiento";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          "Inter",
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI",
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9f6 0%, #feebdd 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(81, 58, 49, 0.15);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .icon-wrapper {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        margin: 0 auto 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7d6a5d 0%, #513a31 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(81, 58, 49, 0.3);
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: scale(1);
          box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(81, 58, 49, 0.3);
        }
        50% {
          transform: scale(1.05);
          box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(81, 58, 49, 0.4);
        }
      }

      .icon {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        stroke: #fff9f6;
        animation: rotate 3s linear infinite;
      }

      @keyframes rotate {
        from {
          transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        to {
          transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #513a31;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: #7d6a5d;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .info-box {
        background: #feebdd;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border: 2px solid #d6c4b6;
      }

      .info-box p {
        color: #513a31;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      .info-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .notification-form {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .email-input {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        border: 2px solid #d6c4b6;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #513a31;
        background: white;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .email-input:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: #7d6a5d;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(125, 106, 93, 0.1);
      }

      .email-input::placeholder {
        color: #d6c4b6;
      }

      .submit-button {
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7d6a5d 0%, #513a31 100%);
        color: #fff9f6;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .submit-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(81, 58, 49, 0.3);
      }

      .submit-button:active {
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      .social-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #d6c4b6;
      }

      .social-link {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #feebdd;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .social-link:hover {
        background: #7d6a5d;
        transform: translateY(-3px);
      }

      .social-link:hover svg {
        stroke: #fff9f6;
      }

      .social-link svg {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        stroke: #513a31;
        transition: stroke 0.3s ease;
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .container {
          padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .notification-form {
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .submit-button {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="icon-wrapper">
        <svg
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          class="icon"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          ><path
            d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"
          ></path></svg
        >
      </div>

      <h1>Estamos en Mantenimiento</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Estamos trabajando para mejorar tu experiencia. Pronto volveremos con
        nuevas funcionalidades.
      </p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p>
          Estamos realizando mejoras en nuestro sistema para ofrecerte un mejor
          servicio.
        </p>
        <p>Tiempo estimado: 2-4 horas</p>
      </div>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Twitter">
          <svg
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Facebook">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path
              d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Instagram">
          <svg
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path
              d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37m1.5-4.87h.01"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Email">
          <svg
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2"
            ></path><path d="m22 6-10 7L2 6"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
